Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.34,0:00:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,While you were away,\Nsecret messages arrived every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.84,0:00:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Secret messages?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.38,0:00:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Someone slipped them under the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.81,0:00:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Are you eating properly?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.39,0:00:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Get well soon."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.85,0:00:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's Lana's handwriting.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.59,0:02:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,All righty then!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.09,0:02:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Health starts with food!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.30,0:02:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I've never been to a place like this…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.18,0:02:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.64,0:02:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't you know? We're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.69,0:02:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm your lifesaver, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.73,0:02:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you grateful?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.15,0:02:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,See.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.24,0:02:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-We're friends, aren't we?\N-Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.74,0:02:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't count if you force her to say so!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.75,0:02:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.09,0:02:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.09,0:02:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My hometown is far from the sea too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.13,0:02:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever we eat fish,\Nwe always have grilled river fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.51,0:03:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Only commoners eat\Nwith their hands, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone eats like this where I'm from.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.06,0:03:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,In between all the farm work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.31,0:03:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you're a noble or a commoner,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.65,0:03:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone has to pitch in\Nand work if they want to get a meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.28,0:03:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing you managed to get\Na place at this academy, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.99,0:03:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, what are you gonna go see\Nat the school festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.08,0:03:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to stay in my room\Nuntil the ball starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.17,0:03:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the answer I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.29,0:03:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Neil is busy,\Nso he doesn't have time during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.97,0:03:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's no point in me participating\Nin the school festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.76,0:03:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But the school play is\Nthe main event at the school festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.22,0:03:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,After all,\NI'm the one overseeing the costumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.10,0:03:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.35,0:03:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.86,0:03:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The way you argued with the history club.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.40,0:03:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And this year\Nthere are even fireworks during the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.65,0:03:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Extravagant, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:03:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.53,0:04:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why don't the three\Nof us go and watch it together?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.24,0:04:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if some people are just lounging\Naround in their room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.71,0:04:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you're donating some embroidery\Nwork to the charity bazaar,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.34,0:04:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-right, Casey?\N-Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.68,0:04:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so talented.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.05,0:04:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.93,0:04:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.10,0:04:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm not bad at embroidery.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.85,0:04:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like me\Nto embroider something for you both?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.90,0:04:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.86,0:04:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're already teaching me how to ride\Na horse, and now embroidery too…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.20,0:04:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not doing it as a favor, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.83,0:04:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I do horse riding and embroidery\Nbecause I like it, that's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.63,0:04:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Horse riding, embroidery,\Nand the school festival…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.22,0:05:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Treasurer Norton.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.60,0:05:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We need help moving some materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.14,0:05:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to the east gate after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.81,0:05:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it for the school festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll handle the wood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.98,0:05:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,His Highness and Secretary Howard\Nwill take care of the fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.82,0:05:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Secretary Greyham\Nand General Affairs Officer Maywood
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,will oversee the costumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.70,0:05:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How careless to leak the\Nstudent council's plans to a third party.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the problem, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.41,0:05:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Neil and Bridget Greyham are going\Nto supervise things together…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.13,0:05:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go and interrupt them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.21,0:05:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.67,0:05:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, come straightaway,\Nas soon as class is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.26,0:05:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Lord Ashley.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.97,0:05:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh, that's a bit tricky, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.27,0:05:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm called "Ashley" too. Lady Ashley.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.23,0:05:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But I call you "Lady Claudia."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.56,0:05:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.36,0:05:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not on first name basis with you,\Nis she, dear brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a friend,\Nso she calls me by my first name,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.07,0:06:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're just an ordinary acquaintance,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.66,0:06:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,so she doesn't use yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.33,0:06:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Ashley is really good at his job,\Nand so amazing…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.04,0:06:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So I respect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're making your junior\Nfeel uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,-How cruel, dear brother.\N-No,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.34,0:06:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.26,0:06:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You can call me Cyril.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.19,0:06:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Lord Cyril.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.15,0:06:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.11,0:06:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What a fuss over a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.29,0:06:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Chicken for dinner today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.96,0:06:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A mana reaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.17,0:06:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness, the traders have arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.42,0:07:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then,\Nwould you mind showing them around?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.51,0:07:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to prepare the reception inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.64,0:07:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The person in charge of stage design
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.31,0:07:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,should be coming to check\Nthe materials, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.52,0:07:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Casey?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,HISTORICAL RESEARCH TEAM\NSTAGE DESIGN TEAM
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.31,0:07:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The person in charge got\Ninto a heated discussion
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.15,0:07:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,with the historical accuracy team.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.11,0:07:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So I came instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.45,0:07:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So many numbers…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.37,0:07:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do the counting,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.12,0:07:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,so can you cross-check\Nagainst the list, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.58,0:07:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The next one is over there… Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.60,0:07:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Casey?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.10,0:07:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.02,0:07:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.03,0:08:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.63,0:08:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did I do it in time?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.21,0:08:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you two okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.18,0:08:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Casey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.85,0:08:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It may have fallen on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Get her to the infirmary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tidy up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.60,0:08:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.07,0:08:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.99,0:08:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That was embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.45,0:08:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.87,0:08:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone else would be\Nin shock like that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.37,0:08:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.21,0:09:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The rope holding the timber together\Nlooked like it had cut marks in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.01,0:09:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You're saying it wasn't an accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.59,0:09:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They were shallow cuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.09,0:09:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably to make it look\Nlike it broke naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.43,0:09:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I calculated how long it must have taken\Nfor the rope to snap.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.02,0:09:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have been\Nbetween five and 15 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But everyone's been extra careful\Nwith traders
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.74,0:09:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,because of what happened last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.28,0:09:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Blades aren't allowed inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Casey,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.08,0:09:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,did you cut the rope?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.51,0:09:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I'm busted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.22,0:09:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.30,0:09:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.97,0:09:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.39,0:10:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I was aiming for you\Nwith the timber because I despise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.52,0:10:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would've thought\Nit'd come crashing down my way…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.82,0:10:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.19,0:10:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.94,0:10:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I've hated you\Nsince the very first day we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.12,0:10:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you hiding from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.95,0:10:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.71,0:10:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember when someone\Nthrew away your tea at the party?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.25,0:10:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.80,0:10:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That was me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-I knew that already.\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.35,0:10:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,At my last school, the other students\Nwould often hide my stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.39,0:10:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I don't write my name\Non my things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.90,0:10:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The only person\Nwho saw me folding that piece of paper
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.19,0:10:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,was you, Casey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.86,0:10:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.91,0:11:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've known since then…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.25,0:11:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Monica!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Nero, that outfit…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.71,0:11:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Looks good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, that's not the point right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.47,0:11:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a strange mana reaction\Nin the west warehouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fire attribute.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's absorbing and compressing\Nthe surrounding mana.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.19,0:11:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This swirling flow of mana…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.19,0:11:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A Spiralflame…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.24,0:11:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know about Spiralflames?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you planning to assassinate
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.37,0:11:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,His Highness?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.46,0:11:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.17,0:11:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Miss Maybell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.79,0:11:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,About the issue the other day…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.84,0:11:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean me playing the king\Nin the final scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.89,0:12:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I already turned down the role.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.26,0:12:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}But it's only a tiny part!\NYou only need to do a few words!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.35,0:12:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Eliane, who's playing the queen,\Nalso wants you to play the part!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.65,0:12:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Any more of this\Nand I'll have to consider it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.82,0:12:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,an obstruction\Nto the student council's duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.61,0:12:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.11,0:12:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the play will be a success\Nwithout me on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.91,0:12:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that smart?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.79,0:12:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Eliane is one\Nof your potential fiancées, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll handle myself correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.05,0:12:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A prospective fiancée\Narranged by Duke Clockford.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.76,0:12:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A pre-arranged shining future.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about any of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.14,0:12:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But I must become king.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.14,0:12:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if other people call me\NDuke Clockford's puppet…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.19,0:12:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let Duke Clockford's puppet\Nbecome king.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.36,0:13:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Was the accident earlier all for an alibi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.58,0:13:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't afford to get caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My entire family\Nwould be executed for killing royalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.21,0:13:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If His Highness Felix\Nbecomes the next king,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.88,0:13:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,then Duke Clockford,\Nwho is supporting him,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.51,0:13:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,will start a war\Nwith the Kingdom of Landor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.34,0:13:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The puppet second prince\Nwon't be able to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.18,0:13:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,When I heard that an earth dragon appeared\Nin the town of Craeme
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.77,0:13:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and was defeated by a passing mage,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.73,0:13:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I was envious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.94,0:13:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no soldiers, no money,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.19,0:13:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and the dragon has brought devastation\Nto our people and land.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.07,0:13:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And still,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.91,0:13:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,this country never once tried to help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.83,0:13:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Landor came to our rescue in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.04,0:13:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no idea how thankful we were.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Duke Clockford wants to go to war\Nwith the Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:14:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He's planning to invade Landor,\Nwhich lies between the Empire
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.30,0:14:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and The Kingdom of Ridill.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I ever forgive them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.18,0:14:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Duke Clockford\Nand that puppet second prince of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.93,0:14:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in real trouble now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,To stop the Spiralflame,\Nwe need the deactivation code.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.23,0:14:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Casey. Stop the Spiralflame!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never stop the Spiralflame,\Neven if you torture me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.45,0:14:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going any further either,\Nsince you are on the student council.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.08,0:14:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This can't be happening.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if I don't do something…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.30,0:14:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't be able to live with myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If being worthy as a member\Nof the student council{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.68,0:14:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is the duty of Monica Norton,\Nstudent council treasurer,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.98,0:14:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}then this is my duty\Nas a member of the Seven Sages,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.31,0:14:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Silent Witch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.61,0:15:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nero, I'm going to attack the academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.15,0:15:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.82,0:15:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.83,0:15:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,When the academy suffers\Nan external attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.58,0:15:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,it activates Louis's protective barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.67,0:15:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you to find\Nthe barrier's activation point.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.89,0:15:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, Louis's barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.01,0:15:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Nero!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.06,0:15:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems to be near the old garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.72,0:15:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.85,0:15:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.02,0:15:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.49,0:15:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The Spiralflame will explode\Nany moment now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.65,0:15:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.16,0:15:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.50,0:15:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I have to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.00,0:16:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Something is familiar…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.84,0:16:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her side profile…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had three older brothers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.02,0:16:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My eldest brother was dropped\Nfrom a great height{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.89,0:16:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}by a pterodragon and died instantly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.23,0:16:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My second-eldest brother\Nwas torn apart by a red dragon,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.65,0:16:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}his body left without limbs.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.86,0:16:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My third-eldest brother was burned\Nby the fiery breath of the red dragon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.87,0:16:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The skin was stuck\Nto the helmet and armor,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.49,0:16:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}making it impossible to remove them,\Nso he was buried just like that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.50,0:16:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her face bears a determination to fight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.71,0:16:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The same expression worn by my brothers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.26,0:16:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-Got it.\N-Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.72,0:16:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We overwrite it to include\Nan anti-Spiralflame formula. Get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.15,0:17:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.27,0:17:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryn said that it was loaded\Nwith booby traps.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.86,0:17:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Monica, look out below!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.92,0:17:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.59,0:17:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A barrier filled with murderous intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.67,0:17:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Just how messed up\Nin the head is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.55,0:17:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't think\NLouis made this on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.56,0:17:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.60,0:17:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I only know one person
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,who can make plants grow this quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.73,0:17:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She is one of the Seven Sages like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.15,0:17:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The Witch of Thorns.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.03,0:17:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So basically, it means\Na showdown against two of the Seven Sages.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.91,0:18:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Monica doing magecraft?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.88,0:18:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We're running out of time, Monica.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.54,0:18:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.55,0:18:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. Not seen that for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.27,0:18:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,In the name of one of the Seven Sages,\Nthe Silent Witch, Monica Everett…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.36,0:18:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Open, gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.03,0:18:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Summoning a spirit king.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.79,0:18:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Although Monica can cast most spells\Nwithout chanting,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.54,0:18:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}some chants cannot be omitted.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.46,0:18:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Words offered to a summoned being.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.59,0:18:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The words spoken by Ralph, the first king\Nand hero of The Kingdom of Ridill,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.72,0:18:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}when he defeated the evil dragon,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.77,0:19:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}are known as "ritual chanting."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.64,0:19:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Appear now from the edge of silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.44,0:19:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wind spirit king, Sheffield.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.10,0:19:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Monica?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.10,0:19:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just you\Nwho has been hiding things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.61,0:19:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dummy formula analysis, release.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.53,0:20:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Set barrier coordinates, complete.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.79,0:20:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about to get messy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.08,0:20:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Change the activation condition\Nof the barrier{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}from "external attack"\Nto "internal attack."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.17,0:20:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Limited to fire attribute.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.71,0:20:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oxygen eliminated!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.63,0:20:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And then, just got to…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.01,0:20:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Compress! Compress! Compress!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.60,0:20:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Compress! Compress! Compress!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.35,0:20:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Compress! Compress!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.58,0:20:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Just in time…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.42,0:20:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Whoa,\Nyour mana is totally drained, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.05,0:20:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yeah, it's been a while\Nsince I've used that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.15,0:21:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so focused\Non trying to convince you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.02,0:21:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,that I couldn't see your true nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.33,0:21:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Casey…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.49,0:21:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't, Monica.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.33,0:21:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a cruel criminal who tried to take\NHis Highness's life, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.75,0:21:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You really need to hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.63,0:21:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, we've got a serious problem here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.72,0:21:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving the rest to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.61,0:21:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You damn, stupid maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.03,0:22:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you so many times to improve\Nyour landing technique, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.32,0:22:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I named it the Tornado Kick Landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.03,0:22:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It has high attack power,\Nand it's stylish.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.87,0:22:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing stylish about being\Nburied up to your knees in the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.75,0:22:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,My barrier was acting up,\Nso I came to check on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.26,0:22:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was you after all, my fellow sage.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.02,0:23:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Translated by Daisy Savage

